textBeforeTable: Specifications   Compatibility All SAS compatible servers including: Dell PowerEdge 1900, 1950, 2900, 2950, 6900, 6950. PowerVault MD1000   30% more IOPS and 20% faster response times than 3.5" 10K drives The industry's highest reliability 3.5" drive Seagate-exclusive IRAW enhances data protection by verifying-during drive idle time-that data in the drive buffer was properly written.   Idle Read After Write (IRAW)   The nonrecoverable error rate has been improved by a factor of 10.   Nonrecoverable Error Rate   Perpendicular recording is fundamentally superior, enabling the highest areal density with 30 percent higher performance.   Perpendicular Recording   Second generation Seagate-exclusive BMS proactively scans the media for potential defects during drive idle time. It enables incipient errors to be corrected before data is lost.   Background Media Scan (BMS)   Delivers more I/O's per second and faster sustained transfer rates than 10K 3.5-inch drvies, enabling the same high performance to be met with fewer drives.   15K RPM spindle speed   Benefits Features
